title: Full Show (Lil Wayne joins the show to preview NFL season, Rams get blown out by Bills)
description:
00:00 Bills blowout Rams 31-10
23:13 Bucs (-2.5) vs the Cowboys preview
51:53 Michael Jordon promotes Tom Brady starting his 23rd season
1:08:21 OBJ attends Rams home opener and pregame banner ceremony
1:16:31 Lil Wayne joins the show
1:30:01 Lil Wayne on Shannon's prediction that the Vikings will win NFC North
1:40:03 Lil Wayne on Pat Bev and Russell Westbrook situation on Lakers
1:49:08 Lil Wayne on Baker Mayfield
1:53:21 Lamar Jackson and Ravens do not reach agreement before deadline today
